casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico.

Motion of the River Master for award of compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded $8,082.13 for the period July 1 through September 30, 1992, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 938.]
